lead_paragraph: Japan's Nao Hibino and Kurumi Nara were among the winners on the first day of main-draw play at the WTA Tashkent Open on Monday as both beat junior players.

headline.print_headline: Hibino, Nara Win in Tashkent Open 1st Round
